OL,3,CRegistered nurse accused of offences
OL,4,Cincluding sexual assault
OL,6,FA nurse from South Tyneside is
OL,7,Fstanding trial accused of several
OL,8,Foffences including sexual assault and
OL,9,Fracially aggravated harassment.
OL,11,FWilliam Malcolm, 61, who is also known
OL,12,Fas Bill, is standing trial at
OL,13,FNewcastle Crown Court. The charges
OL,14,Fagainst him are ten counts of sexual
OL,15,Fassault, two of ill treatment of a
OL,16,Fperson in care and one of racially
OL,17,Faggravated harassment.
OL,19,FHe denies all 13 allegations.
