OL,3,CRegistered nurse accused of offences
OL,4,Cincluding sexual assault
OL,6,FThe name of the residential facility
OL,7,Fwhere it is claimed these offences
OL,8,Fhappened cannot be named, to protect
OL,9,Fthe identities of the alleged victims.
OL,11,FThe court heard today (28 February),
OL,12,Fthe nurse from South Shields was
OL,13,Fracist, homophobic and repeatedly
OL,14,Fkissed and cuddled two vulnerable
OL,15,Fpatients. Some of William Malcolm's
OL,16,Fbehaviour was described to the jury by
OL,17,Fone colleague as "disgusting."
