OL,6,FTwo of his work colleagues called by
OL,7,Fthe prosecution both described him in
OL,8,Frecorded interviews as having been
OL,9,Fracist and homophobic in front of
OL,10,Fcolleagues.
OL,12,FBoth also claimed the defendant had
OL,13,Fdirected foul mouthed personal insults
OL,14,Fat a person in their care about their
OL,15,Fbody and that he had also made
OL,16,Foffensive remarks about the bodies of
OL,17,Ftwo female colleagues.
